title: Sammy Sosa hopes to throw out first pitch for Cubs at a World Series game—report
text: There has been much conjecture as to whom the Cubs might ask to throw out the first pitch if the team makes it to the World Series . Some names being tossed around are Billy Williams , Fergie Jenkins , Dutchie Caray, Vicki Santo , Bill Murray
